dc_title_s: Electric Transmission Lines: United States, Fall 2014
dc_description_s: This line shapefile provides the location, current and previous owners, kilovolts of power, operational status, and other infomation about electric transmission lines in the United States. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for renewable and electric energy in the U.S. This layer is from the 2014 Fall Quarter update (Update 1017).This layer can be used to locate electric transmission lines in the United States.
